  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The residence building is located a 2 minutes' walk to Les Houches centre and 8 kilometres from Chamonix resort centre.</p>
<p><span>It is around 400 metres to the Bellvue ski lift. </span></p>
<p><span>The apartment building is also located 350 metres from the closest supermarket called Carrefour Contact.</span></p>
<p><span>The nearest bus stop is just outside the hotel</span></p>]]></locationDescription>
