  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments </strong>are 40<span>m</span><sup>2</sup> and sleep 2-4 people. These apartments have one twin bedroom, a living room with sofa bed that creates two single beds, a fully equipped kitchen, a bathroom, WC and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Two bedrooms apartments </strong>are 55<span>m</span><sup>2</sup> and sleep 2-6 people. These apartments have two twin bedrooms, a living room with sofa bed that creates two single beds, a fully equipped kitchen, a bathroom, WC and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>are 80<span>m</span><sup>2</sup> and sleep 3-8 people. These apartments have one double bedroom, two twin bedrooms, a living room with sofa bed that creates two single beds, a fully equipped kitchen, a bathroom, a shower room, WC and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen including </li>
<li>Wine storage </li>
<li>Espresso machine</li>
<li>Towels</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Safe </li>
<li>TV with English speaking channels </li>
<li>Beds made on arrival</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers (adults only)</li>
</ul>
<p>End of stay clean included except kitchen which must be left clean on departure.</p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
